title: Magnus Carlsen Faces Kasparov for the First Time
description:
#agadmator First encounter of Magnus Carlsen and Garry Kasparov.

Garry Kasparov vs Magnus Carlsen
Reykjavik Rapid (intro) (2004), Reykjavik ISL, rd 10, Mar-17 
English Opening: Anglo-Indian Defense. Queen's Knight Variation (A16)

1. c4 Nf6 2. Nc3 g6 3. g3 c5 4. Bg2 Nc6 5. Nf3 d6 6. d4 cd4 7. Nd4 Bd7 8. O-O Bg7 9. Nc6 Bc6 10. e4 O-O 11. Be3 a6 12. Rc1 Nd7 13. Qe2 b5 14. b4 Ne5 15. cb5 ab5 16. Nb5 Bb5 17. Qb5 Qb8 18. a4 Qb5 19. ab5 Rfb8 20. b6 Ng4 21. b7
